Program: Discovery
Title: Herbs, pills and potions - part one
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryw8
Last Broadcast Date: 13 January 2005
A series of programmes looking the roots of medicine. Rajesh Mirchandani traces the history of Unani medicine. Unani is an Indian medical system which draws directly on the writings of two Greek physicians, Hippocrates and Galen.